### List Answered Questions for an Ad (Public)
# Returns paginated answered Q&A pairs for an ad listing.
# Pinned questions appear first. Supports sorting by upvotes or recency.
# If the caller is authenticated, `isUpvotedByMe` is decorated per question.
#
# @name listAnsweredQuestions
GET {{host}}/api/qa/ads/{{adId}}/questions?page=0&size=10&sort=UPVOTES

###

### List Answered Questions - Sort by Recent
# @name listAnsweredQuestionsRecent
GET {{host}}/api/qa/ads/{{adId}}/questions?page=0&size=10&sort=RECENT

###

### Get Q&A Stats for an Ad (Public)
# Returns the total number of answered and unanswered questions for an ad.
# Useful for displaying a Q&A count on ad cards.
#
# @name getQaStats
GET {{host}}/api/qa/ads/{{adId}}/questions/stats
